{
"#tag"
:
[
"experimental"
]
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"⚠️ 实验性功能\n命令名、子命令结构、输出字段格式可能在后续版本变更，请勿用于生产脚本。\n内置定价表是公开价格快照，可能过期；金额仅供估算参考。\n欢迎在 https://github.com/x-cmd/x-cmd 提 issue 反馈。\n"
,
"en"
:
"⚠️ Experimental feature\nCommand name, subcommand structure, and output field formats may change in future releases — do not use in production scripts.\nBuilt-in pricing is a public snapshot and may go stale; cost figures are estimates only.\nFeedback welcome at https://github.com/x-cmd/x-cmd\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"stat 从 AI agent 会话日志中提取按 turn 粒度的结构化统计数据，用于成本核算和效率评估。\n一轮 turn = 从用户发送一条消息开始，到 AI 完成全部响应（含 tool call 循环）为止的完整过程。\n每个 turn 提取 11 个字段：input/output/thinking/cache token 数、API 调用次数、人类等待时长、human_ratio 等。\n"
,
"en"
:
"stat extracts per-turn structured statistics from AI agent session logs for cost accounting and efficiency review.\nA turn = from the user sending a message to the AI completing its full response (including tool-call loops).\nEach turn yields 11 fields: input/output/thinking/cache token counts, API call count, human wait duration, human_ratio, etc.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"输出格式按受众选择：\n  text   人类可读：摘要 + 模型占比 + 引用明细 + 异常 + 亮点（默认）\n  brief  给 AI agent 看：紧凑一屏摘要 + 异常打标 + 横向趋势\n  tsv    机器消费：表头 + 制表符分隔，喂 awk/Excel\n  json   机器消费：JSON 数组，喂 jq/脚本\n"
,
"en"
:
"Pick output format by audience:\n  text   human-readable: summary + model usage + referenced turns + anomalies + highlights (default)\n  brief  for AI agents: compact one-screen summary + labelled anomalies + trends\n  tsv    machine: header + tab-separated, for awk/Excel\n  json   machine: JSON array, for jq/scripts\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"会话定位两种方式（二选一）：\n  <file>          直接传 JSONL 文件路径\n  --session-id    传 session UUID，自动在 ~/.claude/projects/ 下查找\n                  优先 cwd 对应的 project 目录，找不到再全局扫描\n"
,
"en"
:
"Two ways to locate a session (mutually exclusive):\n  <file>          pass the JSONL file path directly\n  --session-id    pass a session UUID, auto-resolved under ~/.claude/projects/\n                  searches the cwd-derived project first, then all projects\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"成本估算单位为人民币（CNY）。内置定价覆盖 Claude / DeepSeek / GLM / MiniMax 主流模型。\n未内置定价的模型在报告中标注为\"未估算\"，不假装算钱。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Cost estimates are in CNY. Built-in pricing covers Claude / DeepSeek / GLM / MiniMax mainstream models.\nModels without internal pricing are flagged as \"unpriced\" rather than fabricated.\n"
}
]
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x agent stat <subcmd> [options]"
]
,
"#subcmd:Parse"
:
[
"parse"
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat parse claude --session-id 16dee4f1-08ba-4964-a7b0-7c0073acc1ef"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 解析指定 session UUID 的 Claude Code 会话（人类可读报告）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Parse a Claude Code session by UUID (human-readable report)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat parse claude ~/.claude/projects/-Users-me-proj/session.jsonl"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 解析指定 JSONL 文件路径"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Parse a JSONL file by path"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat parse claude --session-id <uuid> --format brief"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 紧凑摘要，喂给 AI agent 当上下文"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Compact summary for feeding as AI agent context"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat parse claude --session-id <uuid> --format tsv > stats.tsv"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 导出 TSV 给 Excel/awk 处理"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Export TSV for Excel/awk processing"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat parse claude --session-id <uuid> --all"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 显示全部 turn（默认只显示被异常/亮点引用的）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Show all turns (default shows only those referenced)"
}
]
,
"parse"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"解析 AI agent 会话日志，按 turn 提取统计数据"
,
"en"
:
"Parse AI agent session log, extract per-turn statistics"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x agent stat parse <assistant> (<file> | --session-id <uuid>) [options]"
]
,
"#subcmd:Assistant"
:
[
"claude"
]
,
"claude"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"解析 Claude Code 会话 JSONL 文件"
,
"en"
:
"Parse Claude Code session JSONL file"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x agent stat parse claude (<file> | --session-id <uuid>) [options]"
]
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"Claude Code 会话 JSONL 文件路径（与 --session-id 二选一）"
,
"en"
:
"Claude Code session JSONL file path (alternative to --session-id)"
}
,
"#exec"
:
"___x_cmd_advise__file"
}
,
"--session-id"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"Claude Code 会话 UUID，自动在 ~/.claude/projects/ 下查找（与 <file> 二选一）"
,
"en"
:
"Claude Code session UUID, auto-resolved under ~/.claude/projects/ (alternative to <file>)"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"UUID 格式（8-4-4-4-12）"
,
"en"
:
"UUID format (8-4-4-4-12)"
}
}
}
,
"--offset"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"字节偏移，用于增量解析（跳过已处理部分）"
,
"en"
:
"Byte offset for incremental parsing (skip already-processed bytes)"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"非负整数"
,
"en"
:
"Non-negative integer"
}
}
}
,
"--format"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"输出格式"
,
"en"
:
"Output format"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"text"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"人类可读，摘要 + 模型占比 + 明细 + 异常 + 亮点（默认）"
,
"en"
:
"Human-readable summary + model usage + table + anomalies + highlights (default)"
}
}
,
"brief"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"紧凑一屏摘要，给 AI agent 读：异常已打标 + 横向趋势"
,
"en"
:
"Compact one-screen summary for AI agents"
}
}
,
"tsv"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"表头 + 制表符分隔，机器可读"
,
"en"
:
"Header + tab-separated, machine-readable"
}
}
,
"json"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"JSON 数组，每个元素一个 turn dict"
,
"en"
:
"JSON array, one turn dict per element"
}
}
}
}
,
"--all"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"明细表显示全部 turn（含 housekeeping/未被引用的；默认仅显示被异常或亮点引用的）"
,
"en"
:
"Show all turns in the detail table (default shows only those referenced by anomalies/highlights)"
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat parse claude --session-id 16dee4f1-08ba-4964-a7b0-7c0073acc1ef"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 按 UUID 解析（最常用，自动定位文件）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Parse by UUID (most common, auto-locates file)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat parse claude ./session.jsonl"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 按文件路径解析"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Parse by file path"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat parse claude --session-id <uuid> --format brief"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 给 AI 看的紧凑摘要"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Compact summary for AI consumption"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat parse claude --session-id <uuid> --format json | jq '.[].model'"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: JSON 输出 + jq 取每轮模型"
,
"en"
:
"Example: JSON output + jq to extract per-turn models"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat parse claude --session-id <uuid> --offset 1048576"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 增量解析（跳过前 1MB）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Incremental parse (skip first 1MB)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat parse claude --session-id <uuid> --all"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 显示全部 turn（含 housekeeping）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Show all turns (incl. housekeeping)"
}
]
}
}
}

